<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NOMAD GENIUS | International Science-Technology Hub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --lux-brown: #1a0f08;
            --gold: #d4af37;
            --cream: #f4ece1;
            --dark-glass: rgba(26, 15, 8, 0.9);
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            background-color: var(--lux-brown);
            color: var(--cream);
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 30px 10%;
            background: var(--dark-glass);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--gold);
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }

        .lang-switch { font-size: 0.9rem; letter-spacing: 2px; }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.7), rgba(0,0,0,0.7)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1451187580459-43490279c0fa?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 5rem;
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: 15px;
            color: var(--gold);
        }

        .hero p { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 20px; font-weight: 300; }

        /* Section Styling */
        section { padding: 120px 10%; border-bottom: 1px solid #3d2b1f; }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--gold);
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        /* Content Grid */
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 50px;
        }

        .card {
            border: 1px solid var(--gold);
            padding: 40px;
            background: rgba(61, 43, 31, 0.2);
            transition: 0.4s ease;
        }

        .card:hover { background: var(--gold); color: var(--lux-brown); transform: translateY(-10px); }

        .card h3 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }

        /* Korean Section Highlight */
        .korean-hub {
            background: #25160d;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--gold);
            padding: 60px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .korean-hub h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: var(--gold); }

        /* Contact Section */
        .contact { text-align: center; padding: 100px 0; }
        .social-icons i { font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--gold); margin: 0 25px; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; }
        .social-icons i:hover { color: white; transform: scale(1.2); }

        footer { text-align: center; padding: 40px; font-size: 0.8rem; border-top: 1px solid #3d2b1f; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo">NOMAD GENIUS</div>
        <div class="lang-switch">ENGLISH | 한국어</div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <h1>NOMAD GENIUS</h1>
        <p>Global Strategic Science & Technology Hub</p>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--gold);">Empowering the Future of Eurasia and East Asia</p>
    </header>

    <section id="vision">
        <h2 class="section-title">The Vision</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Global Strategy</h3>
                <p>Bridging the scientific gap between Central Asia and the advanced technological landscape of South Korea. Focused on sustainable innovation.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Scientific Legacy</h3>
                <p>Preserving the wisdom of the Altai while integrating it with modern biotechnological and genetic research standards.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="korean" class="korean-hub">
        <h2>K-Innovation Portal (한국 과학 기술)</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.4rem;">Connecting Seoul's High-Tech ecosystem with the Turkic World.</p>
        <div class="grid" style="margin-top: 30px;">
            <div>
                <h4 style="color: var(--gold);">Advanced AI & Robotics</h4>
                <p>한국의 인공지능 및 로봇 기술 연구 데이터를 중앙 아시아의 신진 과학자들과 공유합니다.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 style="color: var(--gold);">Bio-Tech Research</h4>
                <p>서울의 주요 연구소와 협력하여 생명 공학 분야의 혁신을 도모합니다.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact">
        <h2 class="section-title">Global Network</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 40px;"><i class="fas fa-satellite"></i> HQ: ALTAI - SEOUL - ISTANBUL</p>
        <div class="social-icons">
            <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
            <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>
            <i class="fab fa-discord"></i>
            <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i>
        </div>
        <p style="margin-top: 50px; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--gold);">+90 5XX XXX XX XX</p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 NOMAD GENIUS HUB. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
